  "texts": [
    "[2,3,45,47,51,52,57,59,61,63].",
    "However, the auxiliary modality often indicates information that is different from the visible map.",
    "For example, thermal and depth images contain temperature and depth data, respectively.",
    "The aforementioned trackers apply feature fusion, ignoring the modality discrepancy, which decreases the tracking accuracy and causes the tracker to easily drift.",
    "To this end, some trackers differentiate the heterogeneous modalities by applying different feature methods."
  ]
}